            "title": "黑期高水約40點 重磅港股ADR互有升跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時17分升92點或0.34%，報26888點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報26861點，較香港上日現貨收市高12點或0.05%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣624.9元，較上日香港收市低2.64元或0.42%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣162.9元，較上日香港收市高2.96元或1.85%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣105元，較上日香港收市高0.06元或0.06%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣116.5元，較上日香港收市低0.85元或0.73%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣38元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.03%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣127.2元，較上日香港收市高0.79元或0.62%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣84.5元，較上日香港收市高0.08元或0.1%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣431.9元，較上日香港收市高0.06元或0.01%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣69.7元，較上日香港收市低0.34元或0.48%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.8元，較上日香港收市低0.03元或0.41%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指期貨夜市收報26920點，升57點，較上日恒指收市26848點，高水72點。科指期貨夜市收報5900點，較上日科指收市高水30點；國指期貨夜市收報9312點，較上日國指收市高水27點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15580429-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%8440%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e4%ba%92%e6%9c%89%e5%8d%87%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 08:25:29",
